and she'd give me the signal.

682
00:38:57.404 --> 00:38:58.706
Show him, Iz.

683
00:38:58.739 --> 00:39:01.843
COACH: There we go!
Good job, good job.

684
00:39:01.876 --> 00:39:03.611
Green light to swing.

