00:39:03.644 --> 00:39:04.979
COACH:
Wait for the ball, boys!

686
00:39:05.012 --> 00:39:06.147
-Come on, come on!
-(clicks tongue)

687
00:39:06.180 --> 00:39:07.782
-Hey, there he is.
-RAY: Hey, Coach.

688
00:39:07.815 --> 00:39:08.983
Sorry I'm late.

689
00:39:09.016 --> 00:39:10.718
-Hey, guys.
-EVE: Hey.

690
00:39:10.751 --> 00:39:11.719
RAY:
All right.

691
00:39:11.752 --> 00:39:13.988
(whispering):
You got this.

