718
00:40:03.470 --> 00:40:05.438
Way to go. Whoo. Good job, Ty.

719
00:40:05.472 --> 00:40:06.908
(whispering):
Hey, Ellie.

720
00:40:12.813 --> 00:40:14.715
All right, Elliot.

721
00:40:14.749 --> 00:40:17.051
All right, come on.
You got this.

722
00:40:17.084 --> 00:40:18.653
TY:
You got it, Elliot.

723
00:40:19.186 --> 00:40:20.655
-RAY: There you go. Nice!
