737
00:40:41.676 --> 00:40:44.011
All right. All right,
get ready, boys! Get ready!

738
00:40:44.045 --> 00:40:45.478
RAY:
All right.

739
00:40:45.513 --> 00:40:46.881
COACH:
Okay, you ready?

