and they wanted
the good school district,

1038
00:55:05.740 --> 00:55:09.010
but they didn't feel comfortable
using the pool

1039
00:55:09.043 --> 00:55:11.411
because of certain
alleged events.

1040
00:55:11.444 --> 00:55:13.080
Alleged events?

1041
00:55:13.114 --> 00:55:14.916
(sighs)

1042
00:55:14.949 --> 00:55:16.416
Yeah, I...

1043
